'''Brendan Holmes''' voiced the [[Mobile artillery]] officer in ''[[Star Wars: Force Commander]]'' and the [[TT-8L gatekeeper droid/Legends|Droid Eye]], [[Stormtrooper/Legends|Stormtrooper]] and Intercom in ''[[Star Wars: Jedi Knight: Mysteries of the Sith]]''.

Holmes is also credited as an additional programmer for ''[[Star Wars: Knights of the Old Republic]]''.

